Euripid

This project may bundle the k6 binary (bin/k6.exe) for Windows zero-install
convenience. k6 is licensed under the GNU Affero General Public License v3.0
and is copyright Grafana Labs and contributors. The bundled binary is
unmodified. Source: https://github.com/grafana/k6

Euripid redistributes small vendored helper modules under `src/vendor/` to
avoid runtime dependency on third-party URL imports:

  - Papa Parse compatible CSV subset
    Source project: https://github.com/mholt/PapaParse
    License: MIT
    Provenance target: jslib.k6.io papaparse 5.1.1 behavior used by Euripid

  - k6 summary text renderer equivalent
    Source project: https://github.com/grafana/jslib.k6.io
    License: MIT
    Provenance target: k6-summary 0.0.2 behavior used by Euripid

  - k6 HTML report renderer equivalent
    Source project: https://github.com/benc-uk/k6-reporter
    License: MIT
    Provenance target: k6-reporter 3.0.4 functionality subset used by Euripid

These local modules are intentionally minimal and maintained in-repo so runs do
not depend on external network fetches at init time.
